1
00:00:01,140 --> 00:00:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A souvenir?</font>

2
00:00:02,380 --> 00:00:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, we went to
a hot spring the other day!</font>

3
00:00:07,180 --> 00:00:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. Please enjoy it with
the others at your agency!</font>

4
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}STRAWBERRY - PLAIN
CHOCOLATE - GREEN TEA
- Hot springs pudding!</font>

5
00:00:14,560 --> 00:00:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which should I take?!</font>

6
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad you managed to get
a hot springs date out of your work.</font>

7
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The work came first, though...</font>

8
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though you had to
reschedule things here?</font>

9
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, we did manage
to solve the case...</font>

10
00:00:31,570 --> 00:00:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kikira, you don't
want one? Maybe later?</font>

11
00:00:45,340 --> 00:00:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He likes green tea flavor?</font>

12
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, sorry I'm late!</font>

13
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just got here, too!</font>

14
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good evening!</font>

15
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, it took me longer
than I expected to get out...</font>

16
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san said you were having
trouble collecting evidence.</font>

17
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is everything all right now?</font>

18
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, yeah... That's what
had me late again today.</font>

19
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to find
evidence in all this garbage?</font>

20
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry. I didn't realize it would be
so much either...</i></font>

21
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:55,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I really need evidence
for this case, so...</font>

22
00:02:55,690 --> 00:03:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry it's all so sudden. I can ask
another agency if you need me to.</font>

23
00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't say I wouldn't do it.</i></font>

24
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, this sucks.</font>

25
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When do you need it by?</font>

26
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, well...</i></font>

27
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have a meeting
with the client in two days...</i></font>

28
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk about a rush job.</font>

29
00:03:16,090 --> 00:03:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm really sorry!</i></font>

30
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing, Daichi!</font>

31
00:03:21,510 --> 00:03:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You found the evidence in
that garbage heap this quickly?</font>

32
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing! Thank you!</font>

33
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down. You're
gonna pick up the stink.</font>

34
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:35,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fell in love all over again!</font>

35
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kikira-san's amazing, isn't he?</font>

36
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's serious about that stuff, at least.</font>

37
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell Daichi
I was gushing about him, okay?</font>

38
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a lucky guy.</font>

39
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't believe a sourpuss like him found
a partner who really gets him.</font>

40
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah!</font>

41
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jarashi-san, you haven't
met someone who gets you?</font>

42
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this now?
You have someone you like?</font>

43
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't say that. We're just
kind of on the same wavelength...</font>

44
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes it easy to be myself.</font>

45
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean the one from the clothing shop?</font>

46
00:04:15,210 --> 00:04:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah! That clerk I told you about.</font>

47
00:04:19,010 --> 00:04:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've had a ton of fun
choosing outfits since we met.</font>

48
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I see.</font>

49
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's important to have
someone like that in your life.</font>

50
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

51
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you have an interest in common,
you can talk about anything!</font>

52
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jarashi-san, you've been acting different
since the two of you met.</font>

53
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Really?
- Yes. You've been so calm and peaceful.</font>

54
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess life does get easier
when you've got less on your mind!</font>

55
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lucky girl!</font>

56
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of, how are things
for you in that area lately, Shizuka?</font>

57
00:04:54,090 --> 00:04:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like you and Tonome
are still getting along.</font>

58
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're currently planning
our cohabitation!</font>

59
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at you, making it happen!</font>

60
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="32">{\an8}And soon,</font>

61
00:05:07,030 --> 00:05:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CELEBRATE!! AKIRA-SAN'S FIRST SLEEPOVER!
- Akira-san will be staying
at my place for the first time!</font>

62
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Romance has refined your cuteness
to even more powerful levels.</font>

63
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gush even more than I do, I think!</font>

64
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys get along so well.
I guess you don't even fight at all?</font>

65
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, most people
fight with their SOs,</font>

66
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I haven't heard
of you fighting even once.</font>

67
00:05:34,410 --> 00:05:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose not.</font>

68
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did complain about
him being an SD once...</font>

69
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An SD?</font>

70
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was being too considerate.</font>

71
00:05:43,990 --> 00:05:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that sounds about right.</font>

72
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see now.</font>

73
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Tonome's a born gentleman,</font>

74
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:56,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so even something like
that wouldn't turn into a fight.</font>

75
00:05:56,930 --> 00:05:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- True!
- I suppose!</font>

76
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Hello.
- Welcome, Akira-san!</font>

77
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I come in?</font>

78
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I smell roses?</font>

79
00:06:12,570 --> 00:06:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I bought them on the way here.</font>

80
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:20,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so looking forward to staying
at your place, I couldn't help myself.</font>

81
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

82
00:06:23,940 --> 00:06:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll be with Akira-san
all night in my apartment!</i></font>

83
00:06:29,470 --> 00:06:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to make him feel at home!</i></font>

84
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bit early for dinner, isn't it?</font>

85
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I suppose so...</font>

86
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so excited. Maybe I came too early?</font>

87
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... How about a nice cup of tea?</font>

88
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a good idea.</font>

89
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I buy some tea
snacks while I'm here?</font>

90
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no...</font>

91
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's a chocolate cake.</font>

92
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made that yourself?!</font>

93
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... it wasn't that hard.</font>

94
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never had a partner
make sweet things for me!</font>

95
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

96
00:07:05,990 --> 00:07:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's not that impressive...</font>

97
00:07:09,090 --> 00:07:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat it right now.</font>

98
00:07:10,970 --> 00:07:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- It makes me so happy!
- Of course!</font>

99
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and I have whipped cream
to go with the cake!</font>

100
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Wait just a minute!
- Of course.</font>

101
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got the cream right here!</font>

102
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make the tea too.</font>

103
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a vase or a glass?</font>

104
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking I'd put the roses in it.</font>

105
00:07:30,780 --> 00:07:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there's a glass—</font>

106
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold very still.</font>

107
00:07:49,730 --> 00:07:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't want to get
cream on your outfit.</font>

108
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I can lick it off myself!</font>

109
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's all over your hair.</font>

110
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Look at me.</font>

111
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it cold?</font>

112
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- N-No.
- Good.</font>

113
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Akira-san's hands are so kind!</i></font>

114
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart can't take it!</i></font>

115
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is she upset?</i></font>

116
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any whipping
cream left in your fridge?</font>

117
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Yes.
- Would you like to remake it together?</font>

118
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Of course!</font>

119
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll do that, then.</font>

120
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There, all clean.</font>

121
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

122
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- It's delicious.
- Thank goodness!</font>

123
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It goes well with
the black tea, too. I love it.</font>

124
00:08:59,090 --> 00:09:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What could be better than this?</i></font>

125
00:09:03,010 --> 00:09:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To think this happiness
could continue all night...</i></font>

126
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:17,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san. You're quite stubborn.</font>

127
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As are you.</font>

128
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I insist that I sleep on the floor!</font>

129
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot allow you to sleep on the floor!</font>

130
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:30,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll definitely step on you
when I have to get up!</font>

131
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care about that! I <i>prefer</i> it!</font>

132
00:09:32,290 --> 00:09:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

133
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll act as a footstool
when you're getting out of bed!</font>

134
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to wake you up!</font>

135
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're at an impasse.</font>

136
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:47,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why don't we both
sleep on the floor?!</font>

137
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why should we do that? We could
just sleep in the bed together...</font>

138
00:09:59,310 --> 00:10:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it too cramped for you?</font>

139
00:10:01,330 --> 00:10:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I suppose.</font>

140
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Akira-san's in my bed!</i></font>

141
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:10,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And two people
in a single is definitely...</i></font>

142
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I sleep on the other side
so that you don't fall out?</font>

143
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No! That's okay!</font>

144
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:19,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come close to me, then. You'll fall out.</font>

145
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We slept together at the inn, didn't we?</font>

146
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to be so shy.</font>

147
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Having you so close in my usual bed...</font>

148
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">i-it's like I'm doing something naughty!</font>

149
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're cute when you're naughty.</font>

150
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're making me mad!</font>

151
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san?</font>

152
00:10:52,620 --> 00:10:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're awake?</font>

153
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning...</font>

154
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

155
00:10:59,070 --> 00:11:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made coffee. Would you like one?</font>

156
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

157
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was too nervous to get much sleep.</i></font>

158
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I had to go to the bathroom too...
I'm so glad I slept on the outside.</i></font>

159
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I know.</font>

160
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we pay a visit to your parents?</font>

161
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking it might be time.</font>

162
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

163
00:11:27,970 --> 00:11:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are...</font>

164
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we getting married now?!</font>

165
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, but I thought we should let
them know we'll be living together...</font>

166
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Of course. Yes, of course!</font>

167
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I jumped to conclusions again!</i></font>

168
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love it when you get your hopes up.</font>

169
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes me appreciate how cute you are.</font>

170
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You shouldn't love that!</font>

171
00:11:49,690 --> 00:11:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Anyway, I'm going to call my mom.</font>

172
00:11:53,290 --> 00:11:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. Let's set up a time.</font>

173
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- So, you know...
<i>- Yes?</i></font>

174
00:12:02,590 --> 00:12:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before Akira-san
and I move in together...</font>

175
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can we pay you a visit?</font>

176
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! Your father
and Fu-kun will be here, too!</font>

177
00:12:11,330 --> 00:12:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Great! See you then!</i></font>

178
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

179
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- What was that about?
- Oh, Fu-kun!</font>

180
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was that big sis?</font>

181
00:12:20,890 --> 00:12:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she's coming to visit!</font>

182
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- At last, this day is finally here!
- What day?</font>

183
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's bringing a boyfriend home!</font>

184
00:12:32,430 --> 00:12:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

185
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to stand face-to-face
and get his measure.</font>

186
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that, now! He's a good man.</font>

187
00:12:49,930 --> 00:12:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome, Tonome-san!</font>

188
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say hello, Fu-kun!</font>

189
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-kun's here too? It's been so long!</font>

190
00:12:58,580 --> 00:13:01,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san, Fu-kun's my little brother!</font>

191
00:13:01,850 --> 00:13:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pleasure to meet you.</font>

192
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No face, then.</font>

193
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I do actually have one...</font>

194
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's move out!</font>

195
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being in the old family
car is so relaxing!</font>

196
00:13:16,890 --> 00:13:19,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you two ever go out for drives?</font>

197
00:13:23,530 --> 00:13:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's really staring at me.</i></font>

198
00:13:26,710 --> 00:13:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, is Fu-kun a nickname?</font>

199
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Futa. I'm in my second year of high school.</font>

200
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you not often meet invisible people?</font>

201
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I guess.</font>

202
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And why do you have that bat?</font>

203
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- No need to worry about that. Yet.
- "Yet"?</font>

204
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be there soon!</font>

205
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Here we are!</font>

206
00:13:56,720 --> 00:14:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, this is the house you grew up in?</font>

207
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mosaic art tiling is beautiful!</font>

208
00:14:03,790 --> 00:14:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-kun and I made that a long time ago!</font>

209
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It lets me know
the entrance step is just ahead.</font>

210
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

211
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's not so uneven
that it could trip you up.</font>

212
00:14:15,690 --> 00:14:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They made it as a summer
handicrafts project.</font>

213
00:14:19,880 --> 00:14:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. With Dad.</font>

214
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sounds like a wonderful memory.</font>

215
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to hear more like that.</font>

216
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get an album, then!</font>

217
00:14:29,450 --> 00:14:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll have plenty of time
for that later, so let's save it!</font>

218
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on inside!</font>

219
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, shall we go to my room first?</font>

220
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Yes, let's.
- I'm coming, too.</font>

221
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's okay with you, right, Tonome-san?</font>

222
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:53,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- You're so pushy, Fu-kun.
- Is it a problem?</font>

223
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind.</font>

224
00:14:57,870 --> 00:15:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-kun! Take them drinks!</font>

225
00:15:00,830 --> 00:15:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san. Let me
help you up the stairs.</font>

226
00:15:03,460 --> 00:15:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can handle it!</font>

227
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my own house.
I know what I'm doing.</font>

228
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:09,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, do you?</font>

229
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:10,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do!</font>

230
00:15:10,470 --> 00:15:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Then I'll stick right behind you.
- You'd better!</font>

231
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my room.</font>

232
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so beautifully minimalist!</font>

233
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:21,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I take your coat?
I can put it on a hanger.</font>

234
00:15:21,610 --> 00:15:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

235
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:31,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Akira-san is in my childhood
home! It feels so strange!</i></font>

236
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's really staring at me.</i></font>

237
00:15:35,780 --> 00:15:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, Futa-san.</font>

238
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any questions for me?</font>

239
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've seemed rather interested in me...
Why's that?</font>

240
00:15:44,290 --> 00:15:48,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, every time I look at you,
we make eye contact.</font>

241
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you've been staring at me,
so I thought you had a question...</font>

242
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you think I didn't
notice you staring?</font>

243
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... how could I make eye contact?</font>

244
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know where your face
or your eyes are!</font>

245
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True, I am invisible.</font>

246
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you can look wherever you want all
the time! That's cheating!</font>

247
00:16:08,540 --> 00:16:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You're the one looking at <i>him</i>!</font>

248
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it is handy
when you're a detective.</font>

249
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back!</font>

250
00:16:18,450 --> 00:16:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka's boyfriend is here.</font>

251
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think my dad's home!</font>

252
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, would you like
to say hello to him now?</font>

253
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he only just got back, so...</font>

254
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When do you think we should go down?</font>

255
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to the bathroom.</font>

256
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right!</font>

257
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, should they come down now?</font>

258
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've ordered takeout,
so we'll call them down when it's here.</font>

259
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing.</font>

260
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sushi is here!</font>

261
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Akira Tonome.</font>

262
00:17:06,890 --> 00:17:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pleasure to meet you.</font>

263
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sit here.</font>

264
00:17:10,990 --> 00:17:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right!</font>

265
00:17:12,620 --> 00:17:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, eat as much as you like!</font>

266
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat.</font>

267
00:17:17,090 --> 00:17:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Let's eat!
- Let's eat.</font>

268
00:17:19,130 --> 00:17:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll put your favorites
in front of you, Shizuka.</font>

269
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He seems a lot like Futa-kun.</i></font>

270
00:17:23,770 --> 00:17:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- You drink?
- Y-Yes.</font>

271
00:17:27,090 --> 00:17:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the owner
of Shizuka's workplace, yes?</font>

272
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Though it's a very small agency...</font>

273
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you. I'll try it.</font>

274
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is awkward.</i></font>

275
00:17:43,780 --> 00:17:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he's staring at me
as intensely as Futa-kun did.</i></font>

276
00:17:52,820 --> 00:17:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do? I hope I didn't
say something to offend him...</i></font>

277
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you handle whiskey?</font>

278
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry! He's a hard man to read!</font>

279
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:07,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's been looking
forward to sharing a drink</font>

280
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with his daughter's
special someone for ages!</font>

281
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Straight, on the rocks, or diluted?</font>

282
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rocks, please.</font>

283
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:27,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's delicious.</font>

284
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to see my daughter as a kid?</font>

285
00:18:33,090 --> 00:18:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made a compilation of her
pictures and videos I can run.</font>

286
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Oh, I'd love that!
- Be right back.</font>

287
00:18:42,770 --> 00:18:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the food. I'm taking a bath.</font>

288
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis, get ready to take
your bath and sleep, too.</font>

289
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Right!
- Tonome-san, good luck.</font>

290
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My husband's family memorial
video is five hours long!</font>

291
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's quite impressive!</font>

292
00:18:58,660 --> 00:19:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll play it now.</font>

293
00:19:00,020 --> 00:19:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, yes.</font>

294
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the hospital
where my daughter was born...</font>

295
00:19:05,970 --> 00:19:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's adorable!</font>

296
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She didn't want anyone
but her mother in those hours.</font>

297
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:25,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to turn a day trip
into an overnight stay.</font>

298
00:19:25,470 --> 00:19:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

299
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't stop my husband
when he gets his movie rolling!</font>

300
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:34,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Will you leave after breakfast?
- Yeah!</font>

301
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll drive you to the station.</font>

302
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! There's a delicious
bakery on the way back!</font>

303
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can buy yourselves some lunch!</font>

304
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What bakery is that?</font>

305
00:19:44,330 --> 00:19:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's new! You can get—</font>

306
00:19:47,870 --> 00:19:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

307
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san and I have been
dating for some time,</font>

308
00:19:56,700 --> 00:20:00,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we're hoping to move
in together soon, so...</font>

309
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right! We came here
to tell them that!</i></font>

310
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course we're fine with it!</font>

311
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Right, dear?
- Yep.</font>

312
00:20:13,930 --> 00:20:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move in together?</font>

313
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad, did you already know?</font>

314
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I told him that's
why you were coming!</font>

315
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't tell me.</font>

316
00:20:25,750 --> 00:20:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought she was
just introducing him...</font>

317
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't I? I did tell your father...</font>

318
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, now that we're
on the same page...</font>

319
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope to continue our acquaintance.</font>

320
00:20:38,090 --> 00:20:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We feel the same way!</font>

321
00:20:41,370 --> 00:20:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one told me.</font>

322
00:20:45,970 --> 00:20:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so nervous!</font>

323
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry about that.</font>

324
00:20:49,380 --> 00:20:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been home in so long,
I fell back into old routines...</font>

325
00:20:52,730 --> 00:20:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it was so hard to find
the right moment to say it, too...</font>

326
00:20:57,630 --> 00:21:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But they're totally on board
with it! Isn't that nice?</font>

327
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

328
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't think I've ever heard
Akira-san so nervous before!</i></font>

329
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:11,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next, I think I should
introduce you to my pare—</font>

330
00:21:12,700 --> 00:21:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you all right? Was it too hot?</font>

331
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No...</font>

332
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I forgot. But of course!</font>

333
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:25,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to meet his parents,
too! Of course I do!</i></font>

334
00:21:25,690 --> 00:21:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd already met your mother,</font>

335
00:21:29,010 --> 00:21:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which made things a bit more comfortable,</font>

336
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you haven't met my
parents even once, so...</font>

337
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

338
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:40,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How should we approach it?
Should we put it off longer?</font>

339
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:42,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I definitely want to meet them!</font>

340
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was raised in a city
with a lot of diverse species,</font>

341
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but my parents since
moved back to our hometown.</font>

342
00:21:49,810 --> 00:21:53,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's rather far, so we
may have to stay over.</font>

343
00:21:53,470 --> 00:21:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Is that all right?
- Of course!</font>

344
00:21:56,130 --> 00:21:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's a rather particular place, so...</font>

345
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the invisible person village.
Only our kind live there.</font>

346
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The invisible person... village?</font>

